results.description:
Dog Bone Shape With Name Decal - Made to Order!  Get yours in the size and color of your choice.

OVERVIEW
All of our decals are made using high quality vinyl with a gloss finish rated for outdoor use.  Decals work best on hard, smooth surfaces such as windows or mugs.  Application instructions are included with every order.

HOW TO ORDER
Please type out the name in the "notes to seller" section when you check out.  The size of the name will be adjusted to fit properly in the bone shape.

SIZE
Size is measured by tallest or widest points on the decal.  I.E. If the decal is wider than it is tall, the size ordered will be the width of the decal.  We recommend at least 5 inches for rear car windows.

SHIPPING
•All orders from Anderson Engravings ship USPS First Class Mail for only $3 total.  The tracking number will be emailed to you from ETSY when the purchase ships.
•The shipping price will not increase due to additional items, so add as many as you would like!
•Most orders ship within 1-3 business days.

CUSTOM ORDERS
If you would like to place a bulk order or add something special to the decal please contact us through the "custom order" tab in this listing.

For additional items available please browse our shop at:

https://www.etsy.com/shop/AndersonEngravings

Thank you for shopping at Anderson Engravings!!

results.title: Live laugh love burlap wreath, farmhouse ruffled burlap wreath, year round burlap wreath
results.description: This ruffled burlap wreath fits into many decor styles. The 4.5"×12" wood sign has the saying live every moment * laugh every day * love beyond words. Each saying is separated by a dark red star. The style works in farmhouse, country, primitive or rustic decor. It would be great in the dining area or anywhere friends and family gather. It would make a wonderful housewarming gift. At the upper left is a 8" double loop bow made with neutral burlap and red and neutral chevron burlap. The overall diameter of the wreath is about 20".

results.title: silk wrap bracelet- silk ribbon bracelet-boho-silk wrap-yoga-ruband de soie-seidenband-, Live Laugh Love #180
results.description:
Wrap the ribbon around your wrist, knot the ends or tuck them in. It's that easy!

This wrap bracelet with beautiful colors and made of 100% silk crinkle dyed and sewn by hand.

The ribbon is about 100 cm long, 1.3 cm wide and the walk ends in a point.

Depending on the wrist size you the bracelet 4 to 6 times to wrap your wrist.

This bracelet features an engraved tag made of aluminum.

The ribbon can be worn as a headband, anklet or necklace !!

The ribbon should be washed by hand in mild detergent solution, then smooth with your fingers and let it air dry.
The ribbon should be carefully ironed, please note that the position of the iron on "silk" state.
